Package: sqids
Type: Package
Title: Sqids Unique ID Generator
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("sqids.org", role=c("cph"), comment="Original creator of the algorithm. Website: https://www.sqids.org"), 
  person("Cameron", "Hayes", email="c.cash.hayes@gmail.com", role=c("aut", "cre"), comment="Implemented spec for R."))
Maintainer: Cameron Hayes <c.cash.hayes@gmail.com>
Description: Sqids (pronounced "squids") is a small library that lets you generate unique IDs from numbers. It's good for link shortening, fast & URL-safe ID generation and decoding back into numbers for quicker database lookups.
URL: https://github.com/sqids/sqids-r, https://sqids.org/r
BugReports: https://github.com/sqids/sqids-r/issues
